summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and establishing Use, Height and Area Districts for a portion of the northeast one-quarter of Section 1, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W. M., annexed to the City of Seattle under Ordinance No. 77429, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto three new sections numbered 2-233, 10-12 and 17-180, respectively.
